rows.label: tlk41300012_05_msg0001
rows.name:
This is bad...
Are today's business talks canceled?

rows.label: tlk41300012_05_msg0002
rows.name:
A Lysaat got into the merchant ship's
cargo hold, you see.

rows.label: tlk41300012_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I have to go to the meeting,
but I can't send the ship out like this.

rows.label: tlk41300012_05_msg0004
rows.name:
I asked the Avaritia security guards,
but they got scared and ran away.

rows.label: tlk41300012_05_msg0005
rows.name:
That's a welcome proposal!
I'm sure you guys could handle it.
